text: The YWCA is an association supporting women and girls. YWCA or Y.W.C.A. may also refer to: *Y.W.C.A. Hioe Tjo Yoeng College, a government-aided, English medium instruction (EMI), grammar school in Ho Man Tin, Hong Kong. *YWCA Site, an archaeological site in North Kingstown, Rhode Island *YWCA-Rolling Bay Route, a shipping route that originated from Seattle, Washington ==See also== *YMCA (disambiguation) *The Y (disambiguation) *List of YWCA buildings *
